      "id": "9adffdf1_2c84f8d2",
      "file_path": ".env",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": null,
      "message": "Couldnt find a way for having two env files but tried to achieve the same behavior using two compose files. The dev command will now have to run by  \ndocker-compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose-dev.yml up\n\nThis will have the merged config. And by default the command will be docker-compose up which will not have the debug configuration exposed.",
